OL,3,CHealth board moves to highest alert
OL,4,Clevel for second time in a week
OL,6,FSwansea Bay University Health Board
OL,7,Fhas declared its highest level of
OL,8,Fescalation as, for the second time in
OL,9,Fone week, its hospitals are
OL,10,F"exceptionally full".
OL,12,FThe health board posted a statement
OL,13,Fonline confirming it had declared a
OL,14,FBusiness Continuity Incident on Monday
OL,15,F(12 January) morning.
OL,17,FIt comes after a similar statement was
OL,18,Fissued by health board officials on
OL,19,FTuesday (6 January) of the previous
OL,20,Fweek.
