OL,3,CHealth board moves to highest alert
OL,4,Clevel for second time in a week
OL,6,FIn their latest statement, the health
OL,7,Fboard said: "Our hospitals are
OL,8,Fexceptionally full and as a result we
OL,9,Fhave declared a Business Continuity
OL,10,FIncident, which is our highest level
OL,11,Fof escalation.
OL,13,F"We are pulling out all the stops to
OL,14,Fcreate capacity by discharging those
OL,15,Fpatients who have completed their
OL,16,Ftreatment and no longer need to be in
OL,17,Fone of our acute care beds.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
