OL,3,CHealth board moves to highest alert
OL,4,Clevel for second time in a week
OL,6,F"However, services in the community
OL,7,Fare also under pressure so timely
OL,8,Fdischarge of those patients who are
OL,9,Fready to leave hospital is currently a
OL,10,Fchallenge. This is causing a backlog."
OL,12,FPeople are being encouraged to help
OL,13,Floved ones who are ready to leave
OL,14,Fhospital by supporting their discharge
OL,15,Fin any way they can.
