OL,6,F"Hospital's the best place to be for
OL,7,Fanyone needing acute care following a
OL,8,Fserious illness, injury or surgery.
OL,9,FBut staying in an acute care bed once
OL,10,Ftreatment is complete can prolong
OL,11,Frecovery by weakening muscles,
OL,12,Fexposing the person to greater risk of
OL,13,Finfection and generally impacting on
OL,14,Ftheir wellbeing including their mental
OL,15,Fhealth.
