OL,3,CHealth board moves to highest alert
OL,4,Clevel for second time in a week
OL,6,F"Returning home to familiar
OL,7,Fsurroundings as soon as possible helps
OL,8,Fpeople feel more like themselves,
OL,9,Fespecially if they can build up their
OL,10,Fstrength by moving around, sleeping in
OL,11,Ftheir own beds and regaining normal
OL,12,Froutines."
OL,14,FSwansea Bay University Health Board
OL,15,Foversees several hospitals including
OL,16,FMorriston and Singleton.
OL,18,FThe last time the health board
OL,19,Fdeclared a Business Continuity
OL,20,FIncident before this January was in
OL,21,FMarch 2025.
